metadata.name: 1 SQUARE METER
metadata.description:
TO LIVE! LIVE ONLY!

I want to live with all my being, with all my mortality. I would like to live in an area of ​​only 1 square meter; Protect me from the horror of death!

Just as a star can shine for almost eternity in this endless sky, I can wait here with the same patience.

I will not hesitate for a moment to brazenly pray to the creators of heaven and earth to live a little longer—even to eternal life.

Even the proudest person can beg a worthless worm just to live a little longer

- 1 SQUARE METER
